argin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/d9199/customchatbotweb.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/09011/customchatbotweb.avif 225w,\n/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/e46ac/customchatbotweb.avif 450w,\n/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/9b8d4/customchatbotweb.avif 900w,\n/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/542bc/customchatbotweb.avif 960w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/d7e55/customchatbotweb.webp 225w,\n/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/8626f/customchatbotweb.webp 450w,\n/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/131f1/customchatbotweb.webp 900w,\n/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/e46b2/customchatbotweb.webp 960w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/3684f/customchatbotweb.png 225w,\n/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/fc2a6/customchatbotweb.png 450w,\n/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/1cfc2/customchatbotweb.png 900w,\n/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/d9199/customchatbotweb.png 960w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/456f6d6bd8a8cf102ef3dc2beded2a97/1cfc2/customchatbotweb.png\"\n            alt=\"custom chatbot\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">custom chatbot</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>In today's world, process automation has become an integral part of business success. One of the most effective tools for this is a chatbot. But why should you choose a custom-built chatbot over a ready-made template?</p>\n<p>Here are a few reasons that will convince you of its necessity:</p>\n<p>‚≠ê Unique Customer Interaction: a custom-built chatbot allows you to implement unique features that make your business stand out from the competition. This can include specific integrations with other systems, unique conversation scenarios (such as adding jokes or creating a specific communication style, whether formal or casual), and much more.</p>\n<p>üìà Growth and Development with your company: custom solutions are easily adaptable and scalable to match the changes and growth of your business. This ensures that your chatbot evolves alongside your company.</p>\n<p>üîë Security: using a template-based chatbot can leave your business vulnerable to attacks. By developing a chatbot from scratch, you gain full control over your data and its security. This is especially important for businesses that handle confidential information.</p>\n<p>ü§ù Support: working with a professional development team ensures you receive not only a high-quality product but also ongoing support. You can be confident that your chatbot will be updated and improved in line with new technologies and market needs.</p>\n<p>Do you use chatbots in your work? Do you think they can help in attracting customers or perform routine tasks?</p>\n<p><strong>We wish you a great mood!</strong></p>","wordCount"